    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has received proactive rod bearing service using VAC coated bearings and ARP hardware. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock providing exceptional lateral dynamics. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this specimen exhibits zero subframe fatigue and retains its factory-fresh torsional rigidity. A true purist's example in showroom condition.",
